{"word":"G1624 - ἐκτρέπω - ektrépō - ek-trep'-o - Avoid","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκτρέπω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ektrépō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek-trep'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Avoid</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விலகிப்போ, விலகு, பிசகிப்போ"},{"paragraph":"1. to turn or twist out"},{"paragraph":"2. to turn off or aside"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G5157 - τροπή - tropḗ - trop-ay'/5157\">G5157</a>; to <i>deflect</i>, that is, <i>turn away</i> (literally or figuratively): - avoid, turn (aside, out of the way).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}